stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle
    Idle --> Scaling : High concurrency detected
    Scaling --> Active : Resources provisioned
    Active --> Idle : Load decreases
    Active --> Scaling : New high concurrency detected
    Scaling --> Active : Scaling complete
    Active --> LatencyImpact : Latency threshold exceeded
    LatencyImpact --> Scaling : Initiate scaling
    LatencyImpact --> Active : Latency resolved